modName: Aela the Huntress New Head Model
summary: A new skull, face and hair style for Aela.
descriptionHtml:
This is what i consider to be a truly nice looking version of aela, instead of the skinny, ugly-nosed, long chinned \"huntress\" that she was, she truly has some \"muscle\" now. Her skull has been remodeled, i.e. the cheekbones and forehead have been changed along with other things.[color=yellow] All in all this is a fairly simple mod, just move the .esp file to the skyrim data folder then check it in the data files menu and BAM! in-game it goes.[/color]

[color=red] ATTENTION: Neck seam, enhanced lady parts, freckles, makeup and less blocky face mods not included [/color]

Mods used in pics:
Covereyes by MrLenski (for the Eyes obviously)
Coverwomen by MrLenski (for makeup)
Better Females by Bella (lip, eyebrow + eye makeup)
Calientes CBBE by Caliente (lady parts for you nymphos ;D)
More Freckles by Zhoken (very beautiful freckles)
